    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Lisa Belkin's cover article on the backlash against children brought an avalanche of mail. It was high time for a debate, readers said, though many conceded points to both the haves and the have-nots. The real problem, as more than a few saw it, is parents who spoil their kids.</p>
